data.description: Welcome home! This charming 3 bed 1 bath home is ready for you. Featuring an open living area with eat in kitchen. This well maintained home has many updates already completed for you, HVAC serviced Nov 23 and new flooring in laundry room.  Large detached garage w/ garage door opener with new service door and separate storage shed. Conveniently located with easy access to schools, recreation centers, parks, shopping, dining, and interstates. Seller is receptive to providing CCA with with an agreeable offer.
